 15/8 /17 . Set out from Sec-Boi in a Motor Bus at 10.30 A.M. Went to Hazebrouck ; the Leav train left at 12.30 P.M. Arrive at Bolougn at 7 P.M. March to St Martin Camp on the top of a high hill . No cross tonight ; our pass will be redat to commenc on the 16th . No leav from this camp except for Warrant Officer . Put my " crown " up , and bluf my way out the gate ; for not one moment of this liberti shall be lost . A splendid citi this , clean and well order . 16/8 /17 . Got away from St Martin 's earli this morn . Embark at 7.30 AM on the Leav Ship , " St Andrew" . Sail from Bolougn at 8.30.A.M. A rough cross got to London at 3.30 P.M. Went to Australian Headquart , Horseferri Road Drew money got fix up . Went for a walk round the town . I feel like a wild man come to town .
